	â€¢	Senior: 77â€“80% of stressed net value.
	â€¢	Mezzanine: up to 90% combined, adjusted by Mezzanine MVD Stress and Supplemental OC %.
	â€¢	OC levels: dynamically maintained; vehicles must be sold within max 300 days (per operating audit).

