	â€¢	Upon Early Amortisation Event (e.g., breach of borrowing base, eligibility, or performance trigger), waterfall switches to sequential, prioritising repayment of senior â†’ mezzanine â†’ junior.
	â€¢	Reserve accounts step up to fund shortfalls in tax and senior obligations.
	â€¢	Residual proceeds (vehicle sale recoveries) redirected to principal paydowns.

